title: What You Need to be a Happier Mom, Part 2
itunes:author: Dr. Meg Meeker
itunes:summary: If you're not the superwoman who can hold a 9-5 job, cook, clean and get the kids to bed on time every single day, don't worry, you're not alone. John and Danny provide encouragement for the mom who wants to do it all, but finds that's not always possible. Receive the book The 10 Habits of Happy Mothers with your gift of any amount!
